705552f-a.title: Brooklyn: Manhattan Avenue - Greenpoint Avenue
705552f-a.text:
Manhattan Avenue, south from Greenpoint Avenue,
showing at the S.E. corner the Corn EYchange Bank. On the
same side of the street is seen the spire of St. Anthony's
Roman Catholic Shurch.
July 25, 1939
' L. Snerr

704713f-a.title: Brooklyn: Greenpoint Avenue - Manhattan Avenue
704713f-a.text:
Greenpoint Ave., at the N.E. corner of Manhattan Ave., showing the
building which housed the 7th Precinct Police Station in 1880; now (1929) it
is ocoupied by the Board of Transportation operating the city's subway
system.
September 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
